                                                <p></p>
                                                <br>
https://journals.plos.org/plosone/article?id=10.1371/journal.pone.0292075
                                                    <br>
https://pressroom.unitn.it/comunicato-stampa/new-insights-neanderthal-cuisine                </div>
            ]]>
